700489f-a.title: Bronx: Beach Avenue - Westchester Avenue
700489f-a.text:
Beach Avenue, east side, north from near Westchester Avenue,
showing the Atonement Protestant Episcopal Church. The clearance,
in the right foreground, marks the course of the old Clason'a Point
Road.
April 19, 1938
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
